\id MAT MATTHEW Matupi Chin Standard Bible
\h MATTHAI
\toc1 MATTHAI
\toc2 Matthai
\toc3 Mat
\mt1 MATTHAI
\mt2 (The Gospel According to Matthew)
\imt1 Mathai Cabu Kawng
\ip Mathai he tah Jesuh kah hnukbang pakhat la om. A bibi hamla Jesuh loh a khue vaengah Mathai he lamkhong mangmu a coi. Anih he Levi khaw a ming nah. (Matt 9:9-13; Mark 2:13-17; Luke 5:27-32). Amah loh he Mathai Olthangthen cabu ka tael ti tah thui pawh. Tedae kum yacut a pacuek lamkah Khrihca rhoek loh anih kah a tael ni tila a tangnah uh. Tedae Bible cabu boeih he aka daekkung tak tak Pathen amah ni tila tangnah ham om. Hlang hing tah Pathen kah a hnonah tubael mai ni. (2 Tim 3:16,17; 2 Pet 1:21). Te dongah ni Bible aka taelkung hlanghing ming he a tueng sak pawh, a ming khaw a ming sak pawh. Pathen kah a hnonah conghol paitaeh he Pathen hmuen ah a khueh moenih.
\ip He cabu he Jesuh duek tih a thohkoep phoeikah kum yacut a pacuek nah dongah a tael dae kum tah rhep thui thai la om pawh.
\ip Mathai cabu dongah he Jesuh cunnah neh khosaknah, thuituennah neh khoboe, dueknah neh thohkoepnah, Olkhueh Rhuem dongah a thui bangla a koelh messiah tah anih ni, Pathen ram kah manghai boeipa kawng a tael. Olkhueh rhuem dongkah tonghma ol sawmrhuk tluk he Mathai loh koep a thoelh.
\iot Sawt Yoeinah
